#Approach:

Approach (Hinglish):

1. Agar list empty hai ya sirf 1 node hai, to reverse karne ki zarurat nahi hai.
   Direct head return kar do.

2. DLL ko reverse karne ke liye har node ke `prev` aur `next` pointers ko swap karte hain.

3. Ek `current` pointer head se start karega.
   Ek `last` pointer rakhenge jo last processed node ko track karega.

4. Har iteration me:
   - `last = current.prev`
   - `current.prev = current.next`
   - `current.next = last`

5. Swap ke baad normal DLL ki tarah `next` me move nahi karenge,
   kyuki pointers swap ho chuke hote hain.
   Isliye `current = current.prev` karte hain.

6. Jab loop khatam hota hai, `last.prev` new head hota hai,
   usi ko return kar dete hain.

Main Idea:
- Har node ke prev aur next ko ulta kar do
- Aur swapped pointer ki direction me move karo
- End me new head return karo

Time Complexity: O(N)
Space Complexity: O(1)

